{"prompt": "Generate a website for a health and wellness app. The website should be vibrant and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Vitality Hub</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #e53935; /* Vibrant Red */\n            --secondary-color: #f06292; /* Lighter Pinkish Red */\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --light-text-color: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 25px;\n            font-size: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .features {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            padding: 25px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 15px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .cta {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary-color), var(--primary-color));\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            box-shadow: 0 -4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .cta h2 {\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--light-text-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid var(--light-text-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: transparent;\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            color: #777;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        /* Font Awesome for Icons (add this in a real project if you want icons) */\n        /* For this example, we'll use simple text or placeholder icons */\n        .icon-placeholder {\n            display: inline-block;\n            width: 60px;\n            height: 60px;\n            line-height: 60px;\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 2px dashed var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 50%;\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Vitality Hub</h1>\n        <p>Your Partner in Holistic Health and Wellness</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Discover Your Best Self</h2>\n        <div class=\"features\">\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <div class=\"icon-placeholder\">\n                    <span>\ud83d\ude0a</span>\n                </div>\n                <h3>Mindfulness</h3>\n                <p>Access guided meditations, breathing exercises, and stress-relief techniques.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <div class=\"icon-placeholder\">\n                    <span>\ud83d\udcaa</span>\n                </div>\n                <h3>Fitness Tracking</h3>\n                <p>Log your workouts, set goals, and discover new exercise routines.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <div class=\"icon-placeholder\">\n                    <span>\ud83c\udf4e</span>\n                </div>\n                <h3>Nutrition Guidance</h3>\n                <p>Healthy recipes, meal planning tools, and personalized dietary insights.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <div class=\"icon-placeholder\">\n              